strings:
<voice_0x01001007><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Ha ha ha! Feisty! You surprise me!
I never imagined you could squirm for so long!
<voice_0x01001008><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Had I not been healing, I would have crushed you in an instant.

<voice_0x01001009><se_def>Dhoulmagus: But never mind!
It is time we brought this little show to an end!
<voice_0x0100100B><se_def>Dhoulmagus: What a pity it will be to finally say goodbye!
<voice_0x0100100E><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Hwa ha ha ha hah! You will writhe in the unbearable agony of these thorns forever!

<voice_0x0100100F><se_def>Dhoulmagus: What!? Why isn't it working!?
What kind of trickery is this!?

<voice_0x01001010><se_def>Dhoulmagus: ...You leave me no choice!
Now you will face my true might!
<voice_0x01001012><se_def>Dhoulmagus: Ah ha ha! Ah ha ha! Hwa ha ha ha hah!

<voice_0x01001013><se_def>Dhoulmagus: You worthless fools! Prepare to be crushed!
You will never pester me again!
